> > | <#_WHITESPACE: ( " " | "\t" ) >
> > | <#_FIELDNAME_START_CHAR: ( [ " ", "\t", "+", "-", "!", "(", ")", ":",
> > | "^",
> >
> >                                "[", "]", "\"", "{", "}", "~", "*", "?" ]
> >
> >                              | <_ESCAPED_CHAR> ) >
> > |
> > | <#_FIELDNAME_CHAR: ( <_FIELDNAME_START_CHAR> | <_ESCAPED_CHAR> ) >
> >
> > and again below I added:
> > | <TERM:      <_TERM_START_CHAR> (<_TERM_CHAR>)*  >
> > | <FIELDNAME: <_FIELDNAME_START_CHAR> (<_FIELDNAME_CHAR>)*  >
> >
